The Princess of Montpensier;;54;;85;;NC;;During the French Wars of Religion, heiress Marie (Mélanie Thierry) finds that her father, the Marquis de Mézières (Philippe Magnan), has arranged for her to marry the Prince of Montpensier (Grégoire Leprince-Ringuet), a war hero with favorable political connections. Marie, however, is in love with Henri de Guise (Gaspard Ulliel), a soldier who is less socially revered than the prince. But Marie's protestations are for nought, and conflict ensues on the battlefield and in the bedroom.;;Drama,Action,History,Romance;;Bertrand Tavernier;;2011;;Mélanie Thierry,Lambert Wilson,Grégoire Leprince-Ringuet,Gaspard Ulliel,Raphaël Personnaz,Eric Rulliat,Samuel Theis,Michel Vuillermoz,Judith Chemla,Philippe Magnan,César Domboy,Jean-Pol Dubois;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/la_princesse_de_montpensier